# How To Make Hot Chocolate
**This recipe will create the perfect cup of hot chocolate**
| Ingredient | Amount |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Cocoa Powder | *2 Tbsp* |
| Sugar | *1 Tbsp* | 
| Milk | *1 cup* |
| Vanilla Extract | *1/4 tsp* |
- [1] Whisk all ingredients into a saucepan over medium-low heat 1-2 minutes
- [2] Pour into mugs
